ddot.it/this ..kind.. collected
ddot.it/this ..format.. format:graphml
ddot.it/this ..content.. character co-occurrence network of Victor Hugo's novel Les Miserables, nodes with label/color/position, weighted edges, 77 nodes / 254 edges
ddot.it/this ..depicts.. characters of Les Miserables connected when they co-appear in the same chapter
ddot.it/this ..authored by.. originally encoded by Donald E. Knuth in The Stanford GraphBase (file jean.dat); widely redistributed (e.g. via Gephi sample datasets)
ddot.it/this ..source url.. https://www-cs-faculty.stanford.edu/~knuth/sgb.html
